public class BottomActivity
extends BaseActivity

Base class for Activities that terminate the application when they receive a key down event of KEYCODE_BACK.

作成者:
Takahiko Kawasaki

メソッドの詳細

onKeyDown

public boolean onKeyDown(int keyCode,
                         android.view.KeyEvent event)
Call this.exit() if the give key code is KEYCODE_BACK. This means KEYCODE_BACK causes this application to terminate.

定義:
インタフェース android.view.KeyEvent.Callback 内の onKeyDown
オーバーライド:
クラス android.app.Activity 内の onKeyDown
